data.description: Room to grow and then some await you in this HUGE home in Holts Summit! 5 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms are meant for you to spread out in this 1.5 year old home in Indian Hills Estates. This gorgeous home boasts over 3,400 square feet with two large living areas AND a non-conforming 6th bedroom in the basement. The covered deck on the back is perfect for relaxing and overlooking your very well maintained back yard. You'll have to see for yourself all of the great amenities this amazing home has to offer! All appliances, including washer and dryer will convey with the home.Seller is offering a $5000 in credits tobuyers to be used towards closing costs or lender buy down costs.
